headline: insitro Extends Research Collaboration with Bristol Myers Squibb Leveraging insitro’s ChemML Discovery Platform
summary: SOUTH SAN FRANCISCO, Calif., October 14, 2025--insitro, a pioneer in machine learning–driven drug discovery and development, and Bristol Myers Squibb (NYSE: BMY), today announced the next phase of their collaboration to discover new molecules with potential as new treatments for amyotrophic lateral sclerosis (ALS).
